khoon ka rishta ( english : blood relation ) is a 1981 bollywood action film produced by siraj darpan , amar roy , harilal j thakker , kusumlata j thakker on sangtarash internanationals banner and directed by samir ganguly .   it stars jeetendra , neetu singh , amjad khan , pran in the lead roles , with music composed by kalyanji anandji .